						  <h4>Returns</h4>
						</div>
						<strong>
						<p>Our policy lasts 5 days. If 5 days have gone by since you get the product but it arrived with some problem(s), unfortunately, we can’t offer you a refund or exchange.</p>
						<p>If you sell a product via nyerekatech.com and you do not get it or not match with description, <strong style="color:#F7941D;">Please let us know that before 2 hours after to receive the product(s).</strong> To be eligible for a return, your item must be in the same condition that you received it. Your item must be in the original packaging. Your item needs to have the receipt or proof of purchase.</p>
						<p>We can’t offer you a return if an item is damaged after picked either from our office or delivery agent because we can’t know if it is damaged by you while you picked. Check your product before to pick up.</p></strong>
						<div class="title">
							<h4>Non-returnable items:</h4>
						</div>
						<ul>
