							<li style="list-style-type: square;">Items damaged during local pick-up.</li>
							<li style="list-style-type: square;">Other items bought in other ways not shown above.</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="title">
							<h4>Refunds (if acceptable)</h4>
						</div>
						<strong>
						<p>Once your return is received and inspected, we will send you an email or call to inform you that we have received your returned item. We will also notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund. If you are approved, then your refund will be processed, and we will automatically be applied to the original method of payment, within a certain amount of days.</p>
						</strong>
						<div class="title">
							<h4>Exchanges</h4>
						</div>
						<strong>
						<p>We only replace items if they are defective or damaged. We do not offer an exchange, check well the product before making an offer or picked from our office.</p>
						</strong>
