							<h4>Shipping</h4>
						</div>
						<strong>
						<p>It is your responsibility to pay shipping costs for returning your item to our office. Shipping costs are non-refundable. If you receive a refund, the cost of return shipping will be deducted from your refund.</p>
						</strong>
