							<h4>Other rules</h4>
						</div>
						<ul>
							<li style="list-style-type: square;">Returns item must be included all accessories, documentation, etc. delivered with the item</li>
							<li style="list-style-type: square;">Modified items is not allowed in return.</li>
							<li style="list-style-type: square;">We highly suggest all returns are sent via a trackable shipping method. Lost packages that are sent via not tracked methods are not guaranteed.</li>
